                <li>Completed the Braven accelerator</li>
                <li>Are juniors, seniors, or just graduated</li>
                <li>Are looking for a full-time job to start after graduation and are eager to begin the process immediately (if you are applying to graduate school and plan to enroll immediately post-graduation, this program is not the best fit for you) OR are looking for a career-accelerating internship</li>
