                <li>Meet once a week with your PM virtually at a mutually convenient time (typically one-hour meetings)</li>
                <li>Meet in-person at least once during the commitment (in addition to the kickoff)</li>
                <li>Prepare for meetings by progressing in the job application process (2+ hours per week)</li>
                <li>Be responsive, prompt, and diligent throughout the commitment&#160;</li>
                <li>Keep the Braven team updated on your progress&#160;</li>
                <li>#GoTogetherGoFurther with your PM and #FindaWay to secure a postgraduate, career-accelerating opportunity!&#160;</li>
              </ul>
              <p>To participate in the Professional Mentor program, please <strong>complete the following application before <%=@due_date%>.</strong>&#160;You will be notified if you have been selected to participate within two weeks of your submission.&#160;</p>
